ai-atk-s0303a8:1_1: by praise, by fortunateness, by form, by complexion,
ai-atk-s0303a8:1_2: Herein, it is said in the first phrase as stated in the way already described.
ai-atk-s0303a8:1_4: But you can’t fix it on yourself, either inside or outside.
ai-atk-s0303a8:1_5: For the seven bondservants are better than the finer than the land of the sea, firefly in the air.
ai-atk-s0303a8:1_6: Of these, resplendent born from an emblic my net, adornments, and burning fire.
ai-atk-s0303a8:1_7: One who is capable of prominentry, having seen (him), sees what can one do for him?
ai-atk-s0303a8:1_8: yet no nāga kings are unable to lift them out.
ai-atk-s0303a8:1_9: But when oppressed by the seventh and the fame it is possible that no one can’t lift them up.
ai-atk-s0303a8:1_10: even though the earth washed, therefore it was not able to lift out the earth.
ai-atk-s0303a8:1_11: Those who say that there is a better or finer than the great ocean.
ai-atk-s0303a8:1_12: The Linked Discourses on the three in the way already stated.
ai-atk-s0303a8:2_0: The Linked Discourses on phoenixes is finished.
